reviewText: I love it .Both Rock and Jack are great together. It realy keeps your attention .I have watched it 3 times and loved it .It is a joy to be able to watch some thing that is clean and decent .I wish they these kind of movies to day. I would love to be able to get more of this series.
Between McMillan And Wife and Dynasty Rock Hudson starred in The Devlin Connectrion. Great father son detective work with lots of action, Jack Scalia played his son.
